            {q: 'How is "Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock" related to Kadane\'s?', o: ['They are unrelated', 'Stock problem is Kadane\'s on the price difference array', 'Stock problem requires sorting', 'Stock problem uses divide and conquer'], a: 1}
